{"tid":2332522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小粉紅作反丨BTS被轟辱華 強國fans大手筆賣廣告賀V生日","createTime":"2020-12-19T16:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T17:42:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0339909d374985bce5a7434b05f8b6ec03d109b","tid":2332522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"紅爆全球的韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）早前因為獲獎的言論被大陸網民轟辱華，令他們近月來屢受強國小粉紅攻擊。而不少BTS的fans更揚言「國家面前無偶像」，又傳出連中國海關都禁BTS的相關產品，當大眾以為強國fans會「捨棄」BTS之際，根據韓媒昨日報道，有BTS的大陸fans竟然公然「作反」，更大灑金錢在韓國5大著名頻道的10個節目中，購買了12次生日廣告，為本月30日25歲牛一的V大肆慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n人氣節目播出<br />\n廣告將在V的生日前一天，即本月29日上午到午夜期間通過KBS、MBC、SBS、CBS、YTN的人氣節目播出，當中最特別是會在KBS的《李錦熙的相愛好日子》節目分2集播出廣告，原來李錦姬曾在節目中多次表示自己是V的fans，受訪時更坦言希望同V做訪問。據報道指，除了電視廣告外，大陸fans亦購買了地鐵全線7,039條廣告和6,272條百貨公司、便利店、書店電子屏幕廣告，亦從本月19日開始到明年1月1日為止，13輛印有V靚仔樣的大型巴士，會在首爾繁華街區和舉行《SBS歌謠大戰》的大邱進行200米規模的車輛遊行，非常大陣仗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U-VBD5vEbJfThTPkscboEWVfDpU=/802x1360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6HK3ADNLTVCWRMXVZ2ETK5E7IY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU-VBD5vEbJfThTPkscboEWVfDpU%3D%2F802x1360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6HK3ADNLTVCWRMXVZ2ETK5E7IY.jpg&h=eef24ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ahL44v-YCFn5j4RO-NytCISnCKk=/802x1410/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XKFKA3A3HNA4HC5HHOGIJXGGK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FahL44v-YCFn5j4RO-NytCISnCKk%3D%2F802x1410%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXKFKA3A3HNA4HC5HHOGIJXGGK4.jpg&h=fa4d3f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201219/TC6TYZTPYJFXPCYLPPQKFM3QRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201219%2FTC6TYZTPYJFXPCYLPPQKFM3QRI%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=69defdbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201219%2FTC6TYZTPYJFXPCYLPPQKFM3QRI%2F&h=5468fecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201219/TC6TYZTPYJFXPCYLPPQKFM3QRI/</a>"},{"pid":"dad7d9e267ce90938855d315d82bdd0b56aad620","tid":2332522,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"國家面前無偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3be64d6efe6b7643673194761f88a03ced6d7ac","tid":2332522,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:26:34.000Z","msg":"笑4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5050567d3915e9b51557b971b1c307019aed261b","tid":2332522,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"bts戰線"},{"pid":"4b8fbf45bf22625f755bbd995d400af2bc469760","tid":2332522,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"呢啲人一定要判佢叛國罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6468463b473fb30e4a335568cc7bd034cdef95a3","tid":2332522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5050567d3915e9b51557b971b1c307019aed261b","tid":2332522,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"bts戰線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"bts=手joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc9238d0598af6e5ff1510902607540357849e7","tid":2332522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b8fbf45bf22625f755bbd995d40